    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Self-propelled, nonrevenue rail vehicles designed to convert electrical or mechanical energy into tractive effort to haul railway cars.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
